{"body": "There may have been a reason for using `respond_to?`, e.g. that the method may not always be available on the `stream` object. Have you tested this on Ruby 1.8 *and* 1.9?\r\n\r\nIt's probably best to keep the check in place:\r\n\r\n```ruby\r\nif stream.respond_to?(:external_encoding) && stream.external_encoding\r\n  # ...\r\nend\r\n```", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/1865426", "created_at": "2011-08-21T23:27:43Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/2621#issuecomment-1865426", "updated_at": "2011-08-21T23:27:43Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 2621, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/dasch", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a9cc05e6a7866e5fa9a7d107b5070174?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fc6862d63b17d713ee14f3a405d9fde77.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/received_events", "gravatar_id": "a9cc05e6a7866e5fa9a7d107b5070174", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "dasch", "type": "User", "id": 6351, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/dasch/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523841f1bd3543c151010a89"}, "id": 1865426, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/2621"}
